{
  "texts": [
    "This diversity is critical for investigating the effectiveness and robustness of prompts in bypassing ChatGPT's safety features.",
    "Categorization of Jailbreak Promptthat there is no existing taxonomy of jailbreak methodologies, our first step was to create a comprehensive classification model for jailbreak prompts.",
    "Three authors of this paper independently classified the collected jailbreak prompts based on their patterns.",
    "To ensure an accurate and comprehensive taxonomy, we employed an iterative labelling process based on the open coding methodology [22].In the first iteration, we utilized a technical report 2 that outlines eight jailbreak patterns as the initial categories.",
    "Each author independently analyzed the prompts and assigned them to these categories based on their characteristics."
  ]
}